</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <p class="sl gt mb-3">Common Questions</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em">ST. PETERSBURG ROOF REPLACEMENT FAQ</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">
        How much does a roof replacement cost in St. Petersburg?
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Roof replacement in St. Petersburg typically ranges from $8,500 to $28,000 depending on roof size, material (shingles, metal, or tile), pitch complexity, and whether structural repairs are needed. Older homes in neighborhoods like Old Northeast and Kenwood sometimes require additional decking work. Call <a href="tel:8135957663" class="call-tracking-number" style="color:#3B9FD9;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">(813) 595-7663</a> for a free estimate.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">
        What materials hold up best in St. Petersburg's coastal climate?
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
