      <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Standing seam metal with Kynar finish is the top performer against salt air corrosion along the St. Pete waterfront. Owens Corning Duration HDZ shingles offer excellent wind resistance at a lower price point. Concrete tile is extremely durable and suits the architectural character of many St. Petersburg neighborhoods.</div></div>
